r:UserAttributePair.r:AttributeValue: {"Title":{"en-GB":"Dataset Description"},"Description":{},"ValueType":0,"HasValue":true,"RelationshipTargetType":"00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000","StringValue":"This dataset is based on the IDSR Case Based Reporting Form used to record COVID-19 cases and tests by the Ministry of Health in Malawi. The form can be found in the archive for the dataset. This form is based on the general IDSR Case Based form in use in Malawi by adding COVID-19 specific fields from the WHO CRF for COVID-19.
